{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/A_Noir_Adventure.png?t=1726269785\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/Genesis_Noir_Characters.gif?t=1726269785\" /><br><br>You play as No Man, a watch peddler caught in a love triangle with other cosmic beings, Miss Mass and Golden Boy. When your affair turns into a bitter confrontation, you will witness a gunshot fired by a jealous god\u2014otherwise known as The Big Bang. Jump into the expanding universe and search for a way to prevent or destroy creation and save your love. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/A_Love_Story_GIF.gif?t=1726269785\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/A_non-traditional_point_and_click_adventure_.png?t=1726269785\" /><br>With a focus on tactile puzzles and exploration, you\u2019ll experiment with objects in small slivers of the universe to discover how they can be manipulated to progress your journey. Dial a rotary phone; destroy a civilization; plant a garden; improvise with a musician; create life\u2014all in your search for a way to save Miss Mass.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/Debris_Found.gif?t=1726269785\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/Jump_Into_The_Expanding_Universe.png?t=1726269785\" /><br>The Big Bang isn\u2019t just the birth of creation as we know it, it's also a gun blast frozen in time, with the bullet speeding towards the love of your life. You\u2019ll jump into pockets of time, explore moments throughout the lifespan of the universe, and search for a way to change the course of destiny.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/The_Big_Bang_GIF.gif?t=1726269785\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/Witness_the_birth_and_history_of_mankind.png?t=1726269785\" /><br>You\u2019ll observe moments in the history of the universe, from the first microseconds of Life to trillions of years in the future. What will you learn about these new creations, in your search to destroy them?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/735290/extras/Earth_Intro_GIF.gif?t=1726269785\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Seeding","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/88280cce359f99c683590a9b8c439a6a5fb886e1.jpg"},{"name":"Starstruck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/fa71542fd597d4d776281b4d4e57619dfc036199.jpg"},{"name":"Reflection","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/b10619038e88dea10556e383e4b143ff62269f19.jpg"},{"name":"Hunt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/18ab8f4834cb8abf44866e109d373dc531581594.jpg"},{"name":"Gather","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/cac12bbb9f08bfe333eee885d8c466cb20753678.jpg"},{"name":"Thaw","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/eaba1fee2b74190449acfde3d7f40c08ed687ad3.jpg"},{"name":"Improvisations","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/b3b4cf45b0bee38f7216b283132d5437223a72cd.jpg"},{"name":"Collision","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/735290/d7da5287ebc341fbab890cf3c5b7cac5a43e593e.jpg"},{"name":"Voyage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommuni